data.description: END OF THE STREET, THIS HOME BOASTS PRIVACY.  FOUR BEDROOM, TWO AND A HALF BATHS, BRICK WITH VINYL TRIM.  LONG ENTRY FOYER TAKES YOU IN TO THE GRANDROOM WITH A CORNER GAS LOG FIREPLACE, AND THEN FORMAL DINING ROOM, AND KITCHEN WITH BREAKFST AREA THAT HAS FRENCH DOORS TO THE BACK COVERED PATIO.  SPLIT BEDROOMS WITH THE MAIN SIDE HAVING AN EXTRA BEDROOM OR OFFICE, HALF BATH AND LAUNDRY.  IT ALSO FEATURES A MEDIA ROOM OFF THE DINING ROOM.  TANKLESS ELECTRIC HOT WATER HEATER IN ONE CAR GARAGE.  DOPN'T LET THIS ONE PASS YOU BY!  MAKE YOUR APPOINTMENT TO SEE BEFORE IT'S GONE!!
